description: The libraries contained in this experiment come from independent growths of skin keratinocytes primary cytoplasmic extracts, NHEK.  They are stranded PE76 Illumina GAIIx RNA-Seq libraries from rRNA-depleted Poly-A+ RNA > 200 nucleotides in size.
